  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Hightower\" title=\"House Hightower\"><img alt=\"House Hightower.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/fe/House_Hightower.svg/50px-House_Hightower.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/fe/House_Hightower.svg/75px-House_Hightower.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/fe/House_Hightower.svg/100px-House_Hightower.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Garmon Hightower</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Hightower\" title=\"House Hightower\"><img alt=\"House Hightower.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/fe/House_Hightower.svg/50px-House_Hightower.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/fe/House_Hightower.svg/75px-House_Hightower.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/fe/House_Hightower.svg/100px-House_Hightower.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Hightower\" title=\"House Hightower\">House Hightower</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Reach\" title=\"Reach\">Reach</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/10_AC\" title=\"10 AC\">10&#160;AC</a><br /><a href=\"/index.php/Oldtown\" title=\"Oldtown\">Oldtown</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfab2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfab2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Father</th><td>\nLord <a href=\"/index.php/Manfred_Hightower_(Aegon%27s_Conquest)\" title=\"Manfred Hightower (Aegon&#39;s Conquest)\">Manfred Hightower</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Rise_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"The Rise of the Dragon\">The Rise of the Dragon</a></i> (mentioned)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Garmon Hightower</b> was a nobleman of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Hightower\" title=\"House Hightower\">House Hightower</a> and a younger son of Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Manfred_Hightower_(Aegon%27s_Conquest)\" title=\"Manfred Hightower (Aegon&#39;s Conquest)\">Manfred Hightower</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfab2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfab2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Character\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Character</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Family\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Family</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Character\">Character</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Garmon_Hightower&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Character\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>During the <a href=\"/index.php/First_Dornish_War\" title=\"First Dornish War\">First Dornish War</a>, Archmaester <a href=\"/index.php/Gyldayn\" title=\"Gyldayn\">Gyldayn</a> describes Garmon Hightower as a young boy.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfab2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfab2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Garmon_Hightower&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>In <a href=\"/index.php/10_AC\" title=\"10 AC\">10&#160;AC</a> during the <a href=\"/index.php/First_Dornish_War\" title=\"First Dornish War\">First Dornish War</a>, Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Manfred_Hightower_(Aegon%27s_Conquest)\" title=\"Manfred Hightower (Aegon&#39;s Conquest)\">Manfred Hightower</a> dispatched his eldest son, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Addam_Hightower\" title=\"Addam Hightower\">Addam</a>, to lead a host against Lord <a href=\"/index.php/House_Fowler\" title=\"House Fowler\">Fowler</a> at <a href=\"/index.php/Nightsong\" title=\"Nightsong\">Nightsong</a>. With most of the Hightower strength away, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Joffrey_Dayne\" title=\"Joffrey Dayne\">Joffrey Dayne</a> led a second army against <a href=\"/index.php/Oldtown\" title=\"Oldtown\">Oldtown</a>. The young Garmon led a sortie against the <a href=\"/index.php/Dornishmen\" title=\"Dornishmen\">Dornishmen</a>, but he was slain in battle by Ser Joffrey.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfab2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfab2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Garmon_Hightower&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Family\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Garmon was the younger son of Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Manfred_Hightower_(Aegon%27s_Conquest)\" title=\"Manfred Hightower (Aegon&#39;s Conquest)\">Manfred Hightower</a>. He had several brothers and sisters, including Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Addam_Hightower\" title=\"Addam Hightower\">Addam</a>, who succeeded their father as the <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_the_Hightower\" title=\"Lord of the Hightower\">Lord of the Hightower</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfab2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfab2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div style=\"overflow:auto;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:separate;font: 90% sans-serif;\">\n<tbody><tr align=\"center\"><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\"><a href=\"/index.php/Manfred_Hightower_(Aegon%27s_Conquest)\" title=\"Manfred Hightower (Aegon&#39;s Conquest)\">Manfred</a></td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black\"><div style=\"width:2em;height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\">Unknown<br />wife</td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td></tr><tr align=\"center\"><td style=\"border-right:1px solid black\"><div style=\"width:1em;height:1em\"><span s